	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Oct 13th 7:24 PM</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I played a DE cleric. She of course worshipped Innoruuk. So when I got tired of all the BS around Neriak I decided to find a new home. I went to Qeynos. They are very tolerant there. But I had a problem. The cleric guild viewed me dubiously(while merchants&guards loved me). I decided to do quests to change this. I did the blessed oil quest around 50 times, and killed rabid animals to turn in the pelt.. Still no faction change, they viewed me dubiously. As you may or may not know when you turn in Moonstones you get a faction upgrade with PriestofLife. And I turned in a lot of fangs. Still nothing. I gave up. So I do believe there is a cap on faction. And I hope this helps clear up any questions. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
